title: Baker Mayfield vs. Hue Jackson, what's wrong with Aaron Rodgers? (Football 11/27)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn to break down the Titans-Texans tilt on Monday night (1:00), the AFC playoff picture (11:30), Brady's big fine (15:00), Melvin Gordon's injury (21:30), Lamar Jackson vs. Joe Flacco (27:30), Baker Mayfield vs. Hue Jackson (31:30), Kliff Kingsbury's future (36:00), Mack Brown at North Carolina (38:00), Redskins playoff hopes (41:15), if the Panthers are done (43:40) and who is to blame for the Packers struggles (46:15).
